title: X Factor 2015: Cheryl Fernandez-Versini not keen on Louis Walsh return - Ilkley Gazette
text:
Cheryl Fernandez-Versini has said she doesn't think it's a good idea to have Louis Walsh as a "fifth judge" on The X Factor. The Irish music manager, who was on the panel for 10 years before leaving after the 2014 series, has been tipped to return for a guest stint during the live shows of the ITV singing programme.
 Ilkley Gazette.
